{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"msg_1774144660905_b84eywvjr5e","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"glm-4.7","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"call_8f161021af9146429a907af9","name":"Bash","input":{"command":"cat > /Users/wylonyu/selfProjects/PrizmClaw/.prizmkit/specs/018-web-telegram-bidirectional-sync/agents/orchestrator.md << 'EOF'\n# Orchestrator\n\n## FINDINGS\n- Web端使用 `chat-service.js` + `codebuddy adapter`，完全独立\n- Telegram端使用 `ai-cli-service.js`，sessionKey格式为 `telegram:{chatId}`\n- Web端sessionKey格式为 `web:{sessionId}`，两套系统隔离\n- `realtime-hub.js` 已存在，支持订阅/发布模式\n- `session-store.js` 统一管理所有会话数据\n\n## DECISIONS\n- 新增 `session-bind.js` 服务管理Web <-> Telegram绑定\n- 新增 `message-router.js` 统一消息处理器，使用 `executeAiCli()`\n- 保留 `chat-service.js` 但添加弃用警告，支持渐进式迁移\n- sessionKey策略：绑定后统一使用 `telegram:{chatId}`\n\n## INTERFACES_DISCOVERED\n- `ai-cli-service.executeAiCli({ sessionId, prompt, hooks })`\n- `sessionStore.append(sessionKey, role, content)`\n- `sessionStore.toPrompt(sessionKey, channel)`\n- `realtimeHub.subscribe(sessionKey, listener)`\n- `realtimeHub.publish(sessionKey, event)`\n\n## CONTEXT_BUILT\n- plan.md created with 5 phases, 16 tasks\n- context-snapshot.md exists with all source files\n- Phase 0.5 (Agent Knowledge) complete\n- Phase 1 (Context Snapshot) - EXISTS, skipped rewrite\n- Phase 2 (Plan) - CREATED\nEOF","description":"Update orchestrator knowledge"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":59551,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":0},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"94710a11-4ada-4b2b-b382-cda110153e6d","uuid":"07cd5171-e43b-4548-bcf9-ee6fadd1d6eb"}
